OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy across Scotland and Northern
OL,7,FIreland, with rain becoming more
OL,8,Fpersistent as we head into the early
OL,9,Fhours. Dry elsewhere, with some patchy
OL,10,Flow cloud and hill fog developing in
OL,11,Fplaces. A milder night for most.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FRain across the northwest
OL,14,Fmaking slow progress southeastwards
OL,15,Fduring Thursday. Much of England and
OL,16,FWales though remaining dry with
OL,17,Fsunniest skies in the east. Feeling
OL,18,Fwarm away from the northwest.
